= Point Mall Extension =

This is a useful chrome extension for credit card users.

== Supported credit card issuers and point malls ==
* Orient Corporation (2013/04/23)
* Aeon Credit Service (2013/05/11)
* Sumitomo Mitsui Card Company, Limited (planned)

== Install ==
* Orico Extension (Orient Corporation)
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/mgipfpmhgmdldipdgnblmmeopfjafclk?hl=ja

* イオンカード ときめきポイントTOWN (Aeon Credit Service)
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/imcafbgifioikehldallgbmdafcimkpb?hl=ja

== Development environment ==
* Windows 8 64 bit
* Visual Studio 2013 Update 2 RC
* TypeScript (ECMAScript 5)
* Chrome

